query:
UPDATE sota_references SET
                    association_name = $2,
                    region_name = $3,
                    summit_name = $4,
                    summit_name_j = $5,
                    city = $6,
                    city_j = $7,
                    alt_m = $8,
                    alt_ft = $9,
                    grid_ref1 = $10,
                    grid_ref2 = $11,
                    longitude = $12, 
                    latitude = $13,
                    maidenhead = $14,
                    points = $15,
                    bonus_points = $16,
                    valid_from = $17,
                    valid_to = $18,
                    activation_count = $19,
                    activation_date = $20,
                    activation_call = $21
                WHERE summit_code = $1
